<p xml:id="subtitle1" begin="3753749t" end="30864166t" region="region0" style="style0">[주제곡]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle2" begin="222305416t" end="235234999t" region="region0" style="style0">[천둥이 우르릉 울린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle3" begin="290290000t" end="301134166t" region="region0" style="style0">[천둥이 우르릉 울린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle4" begin="351601250t" end="364947916t" region="region0" style="style0">[천둥이 우르릉 울린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle5" begin="382048332t" end="390390000t" region="region0" style="style0">[비명]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle6" begin="393309582t" end="415832082t" region="region0" style="style0">[분노에 찬 비명]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle7" begin="416666250t" end="431264166t" region="region0" style="style0">[실성한 듯 웃는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle8" begin="439605832t" end="449615832t" region="region0" style="style0">[천둥이 우르릉 울린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle9" begin="465047916t" end="475892082t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>일어날 시간이야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle10" begin="482982499t" end="492992499t" region="region0" style="style0">[놀라는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle11" begin="583916666t" end="597263332t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle12" begin="617283332t" end="628961666t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>어둠이었어<br/>[옅은 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle13" begin="644393750t" end="653986666t" region="region0" style="style0">어둠?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle14" begin="664830832t" end="679845832t" region="region0" style="style0">언제 끝날지 모르는</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle15" begin="689438750t" end="700700000t" region="region0" style="style0">끝없는 어둠</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle16" begin="723222500t" end="737820416t" region="region0" style="style0">한없는 슬픔</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle17" begin="739488750t" end="754920832t" region="region0" style="style0">분노, 좌절</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle18" begin="769101666t" end="781197082t" region="region0" style="style0">그런 느낌들</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle19" begin="815815000t" end="840839999t" region="region0" style="style0">그리고 봉구 쌤이 보였어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle20" begin="890472916t" end="909658749t" region="region0" style="style0">이제야 사라진 아이들이 기억나</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle21" begin="927176249t" end="940105832t" region="region0" style="style0">왜 그렇게 된 건지도...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle22" begin="950532916t" end="959708749t" region="region0" style="style0">[휴대전화 문자 수신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle23" begin="975140832t" end="984316666t" region="region0" style="style0">[옅은 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle24" begin="1012261249t" end="1046044999t" region="region0" style="style0">며칠 전에 실종된 애들 이름이랑<br/>사진을 지라시에 올렸거든</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle25" begin="1048547499t" end="1067316249t" region="region0" style="style0">그런데 그 애들<br/>안다는 사람이 나타났어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle26" begin="1083999582t" end="1092341250t" region="region0" style="style0">[옅은 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle27" begin="1093175416t" end="1102351250t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle28" begin="1103185416t" end="1124873750t" region="region0" style="style0">(낯선 사람)</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle29" begin="1138637500t" end="1154903750t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>아, 우리 학교에<br/>특별반이 있었나?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle30" begin="1159908750t" end="1172004166t" region="region0" style="style0">왜 한 번도 못 들어 봤지?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle31" begin="1184099582t" end="1212878332t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>특별반이 있었으면<br/>내가 벌써 알았겠지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle32" begin="1225807916t" end="1252084166t" region="region0" style="style0">냄새가 나, 기분 나쁜 냄새가</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle33" begin="1262928332t" end="1271270000t" region="region0" style="style0">[휴대전화 문자 수신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle34" begin="1273355416t" end="1281697082t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle35" begin="1320902916t" end="1331747082t" region="region0" style="style0">(낯선 사람)</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle36" begin="1339671666t" end="1366365000t" region="region0" style="style0">[긴장되는 음악]<br/>(상우)</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle37" begin="1504002500t" end="1518600416t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle38" begin="1519434582t" end="1528193332t" region="region0" style="style0">[봉구의 옅은 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle39" begin="1643725416t" end="1652067082t" region="region0" style="style0">[음산한 효과음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle40" begin="1664162500t" end="1672504166t" region="region0" style="style0">쟤네들...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle41" begin="1676675000t" end="1692941249t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>사진에서 봤던 애들이잖아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle42" begin="1744242499t" end="1752584166t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>뭐...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle43" begin="1763845416t" end="1774689582t" region="region0" style="style0">잘못된 거라도?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle44" begin="1804302499t" end="1819734582t" region="region0" style="style0">(게슈타포)<br/>[한숨 쉬며]<br/>야, 이 녀석들아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle45" begin="1824322499t" end="1832664166t" region="region0" style="style0">너희들은</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle46" begin="1834332499t" end="1858106249t" region="region0" style="style0">지라시니 뭐니<br/>이상한 사이트를 만들어 가지고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle47" begin="1864779582t" end="1878543332t" region="region0" style="style0">학교 분위기를 흐려?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle48" begin="1883965416t" end="1894392499t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>죄송합니다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle49" begin="1901482916t" end="1923171249t" region="region0" style="style0">나쁜 뜻을 품고<br/>그런 것도 아닌데요, 뭐</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle50" begin="1924005416t" end="1945276666t" region="region0" style="style0">(게슈타포)<br/>우리 봉구 선생이<br/>말해 주지 않았으면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle51" begin="1947779166t" end="1969884582t" region="region0" style="style0">우리는 그런 사이트<br/>있는 줄도 몰랐다고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle52" begin="1985316666t" end="1993658332t" region="region0" style="style0">야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle53" begin="1997829166t" end="2008673332t" region="region0" style="style0">그리고 너 강예림</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle54" begin="2014512499t" end="2044542499t" region="region0" style="style0">너는 왜 이런 녀석이랑<br/>뭘 하고 다니는 거야?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle55" begin="2046627916t" end="2062059999t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>예림이는, 아니...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle56" begin="2072487082t" end="2089170416t" region="region0" style="style0">반장은 아무 잘못 없습니다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle57" begin="2092089999t" end="2108356249t" region="region0" style="style0">제가 반장을 꾀어낸 거고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle58" begin="2115029582t" end="2130878749t" region="region0" style="style0">지라시도 제가 만든 거예요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle59" begin="2133798332t" end="2152567082t" region="region0" style="style0">[잔잔한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle60" begin="2178009166t" end="2188853332t" region="region0" style="style0">죄송합니다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle61" begin="2221385832t" end="2236400832t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림이 살짝 웃는다]<br/>[봉구의 옅은 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle62" begin="2242240000t" end="2251415832t" region="region0" style="style0">이번은</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle63" begin="2256003750t" end="2273521250t" region="region0" style="style0">그냥 봐주기로 하시죠, 김 선생님</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle64" begin="2274355416t" end="2283114166t" region="region0" style="style0">[게슈타포의 깊은 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle65" begin="2284365416t" end="2298546250t" region="region0" style="style0">(게슈타포)<br/>우리 한 선생<br/>[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle66" begin="2299380416t" end="2316480832t" region="region0" style="style0">천사표가 따로 없다니까</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle67" begin="2331912916t" end="2342757082t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>강예림, 서상우</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle68" begin="2351932916t" end="2364862500t" region="region0" style="style0">이제 다시는 안 하는 거다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle69" begin="2375706666t" end="2390721666t" region="region0" style="style0">그 지라시 사이트도 삭제하고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle70" begin="2395726666t" end="2409907500t" region="region0" style="style0">- (예림) 네<br/>- (상우) 네</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle71" begin="2414078332t" end="2423671250t" region="region0" style="style0">그래도</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle72" begin="2428676250t" end="2444525416t" region="region0" style="style0">그냥 넘어갈 수는 없으니까</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle73" begin="2462877082t" end="2482897082t" region="region0" style="style0">반성문 몇 장 쓰는 걸로 끝낼까?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle74" begin="2499997500t" end="2510007500t" region="region0" style="style0">감사합니다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle75" begin="2520434582t" end="2530444582t" region="region0" style="style0">[봉구가 옅은 숨을 들이마신다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle76" begin="2537535000t" end="2557972082t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle77" begin="2602182916t" end="2610941666t" region="region0" style="style0">[옅은 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle78" begin="2622202916t" end="2641388750t" region="region0" style="style0">[삐 소리가 귓가에 맴돈다]<br/>[예림의 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle79" begin="2650147500t" end="2658489166t" region="region0" style="style0">[고통스러운 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle80" begin="2673504166t" end="2694358332t" region="region0" style="style0">[고통스러운 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle81" begin="2769016250t" end="2794875416t" region="region0" style="style0">[거친 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle82" begin="2801131666t" end="2815312500t" region="region0" style="style0">[고통스러운 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle83" begin="2816146666t" end="2829910416t" region="region0" style="style0">[삐 소리가 귓가에 맴돈다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle84" begin="2830744582t" end="2849513332t" region="region0" style="style0">[긴장되는 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle85" begin="2873287082t" end="2891638750t" region="region0" style="style0">[분위기가 고조되는 음악]<br/>[떨리는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle86" begin="2896226666t" end="2908739166t" region="region0" style="style0">(가짜 예림)<br/>강예림<br/>[목소리가 메아리친다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle87" begin="2928759166t" end="2938352082t" region="region0" style="style0">야<br/>[목소리가 메아리친다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle88" begin="2942940000t" end="2954618332t" region="region0" style="style0">안 들려?<br/>[목소리가 메아리친다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle89" begin="3002582916t" end="3012592916t" region="region0" style="style0">[떨리는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle90" begin="3024688332t" end="3036783750t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림의 놀라는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle91" begin="3045542500t" end="3058055000t" region="region0" style="style0">(가짜 예림)<br/>피곤하지 않니?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle92" begin="3070567500t" end="3085165416t" region="region0" style="style0">그렇게 착한 척</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle93" begin="3089753332t" end="3106019582t" region="region0" style="style0">모범생인 척 사는 거</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle94" begin="3121451666t" end="3130210416t" region="region0" style="style0">[떨리는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle95" begin="3149813332t" end="3159406250t" region="region0" style="style0">놀라지 마</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle96" begin="3171501666t" end="3199446250t" region="region0" style="style0">조만간 내가 나갈 거니까<br/>[예림의 떨리는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle97" begin="3209456250t" end="3224054166t" region="region0" style="style0">[가짜 예림의 코웃음]<br/>[예림의 떨리는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle98" begin="3231561666t" end="3243240000t" region="region0" style="style0">[삐 소리가 귓가에 맴돈다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle99" begin="3257837916t" end="3267430832t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림의 비명]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle100" begin="3272852916t" end="3290787500t" region="region0" style="style0">[고통스러운 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle101" begin="3297877916t" end="3320817500t" region="region0" style="style0">[고통스러운 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle102" begin="3345842500t" end="3354601250t" region="region0" style="style0">[옅은 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle103" begin="3504751249t" end="3523519999t" region="region0" style="style0">[음산한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle104" begin="3531027499t" end="3540203332t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>얘들아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle105" begin="3571484582t" end="3592338749t" region="region0" style="style0">[다가오는 발걸음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle106" begin="3631544582t" end="3642805832t" region="region0" style="style0">[봉구가 옅은 숨을 들이켠다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle107" begin="3668247916t" end="3677840832t" region="region0" style="style0">[문이 쾅 닫힌다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle108" begin="3688684999t" end="3707036666t" region="region0" style="style0">[다가오는 발걸음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle109" begin="3727890832t" end="3736649582t" region="region0" style="style0">[봉구의 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle110" begin="3780026249t" end="3792955832t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>반장이 여기 웬일이지?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle111" begin="3820066249t" end="3838000832t" region="region0" style="style0">어제 여기에 앉아 있던 아이들</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle112" begin="3860940416t" end="3873035832t" region="region0" style="style0">다 어디로 갔죠?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle113" begin="3880543332t" end="3903899999t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]<br/>다들</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle114" begin="3915578332t" end="3928507916t" region="region0" style="style0">집에 갈 시간이잖아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle115" begin="3946859582t" end="3956035416t" region="region0" style="style0">그 아이들</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle116" begin="3971050416t" end="3984814166t" region="region0" style="style0">진짜가 아니었어요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle117" begin="4083662916t" end="4094924166t" region="region0" style="style0">너처럼 말이야?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle118" begin="4109104999t" end="4117446666t" region="region0" style="style0">네?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle119" begin="4126205416t" end="4135381249t" region="region0" style="style0">강예림</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle120" begin="4146225416t" end="4167913749t" region="region0" style="style0">지금 네 모습도<br/>진짜로 보이지는 않아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle121" begin="4175004166t" end="4199612082t" region="region0" style="style0">[긴장되는 음악]<br/>쌤 뭐예요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle122" begin="4220049166t" end="4231727499t" region="region0" style="style0">대체 누구세요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle123" begin="4243822916t" end="4263008749t" region="region0" style="style0">[숨을 들이켜며]<br/>그건</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle124" begin="4274269999t" end="4288033749t" region="region0" style="style0">내가 묻고 싶은 말인데?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle125" begin="4300963332t" end="4310139166t" region="region0" style="style0">넌 누구니?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle126" begin="4352264582t" end="4366862500t" region="region0" style="style0">[똑딱똑딱]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle127" begin="4416078332t" end="4424420000t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림의 옅은 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle128" begin="4429007916t" end="4453198750t" region="region0" style="style0">그 애들을 찾으려는 이유가 뭘까?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle129" begin="4470299166t" end="4480309166t" region="region0" style="style0">단순한</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle130" begin="4486982500t" end="4495741250t" region="region0" style="style0">호기심?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle131" begin="4505751250t" end="4514927082t" region="region0" style="style0">아니면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle132" begin="4524102916t" end="4539117916t" region="region0" style="style0">반장으로서의 책임감?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle133" begin="4555384166t" end="4572484582t" region="region0" style="style0">[잔잔한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle134" begin="4585414166t" end="4612941666t" region="region0" style="style0">저희는 같은 반 친구니까요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle135" begin="4620449166t" end="4628790832t" region="region0" style="style0">그건</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle136" begin="4640886250t" end="4651313332t" region="region0" style="style0">책임감인가?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle137" begin="4665077082t" end="4674252916t" region="region0" style="style0">강예림</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle138" begin="4682594582t" end="4707202500t" region="region0" style="style0">네 안에 다른 목소리가 느껴져</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle139" begin="4708870832t" end="4731810416t" region="region0" style="style0">[긴장되는 음악]<br/>지금 네가 하고 있는 행동들</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle140" begin="4744322916t" end="4766011250t" region="region0" style="style0">전부 가식 같거든</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle141" begin="4778523750t" end="4788533750t" region="region0" style="style0">[봉구가 숨을 들이켠다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle142" begin="4795624166t" end="4813975832t" region="region0" style="style0">착한 아이 콤플렉스인가?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle143" begin="4848593750t" end="4861106250t" region="region0" style="style0">(기철)<br/>나오라고, 씨</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle144" begin="4871950416t" end="4880292082t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림의 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle145" begin="4881126250t" end="4903231666t" region="region0" style="style0">안 그래도 필호가<br/>갖고 싶은 거 있으면<br/>[예림의 코웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle146" begin="4904065832t" end="4917829582t" region="region0" style="style0">계속 말만 하라 그래서<br/>[재수가 중얼거린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle147" begin="4922000416t" end="4930759166t" region="region0" style="style0">[비웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle148" begin="4956618332t" end="4965794166t" region="region0" style="style0">[비웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle149" begin="4995824166t" end="5005417082t" region="region0" style="style0">저 역시</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle150" begin="5022934582t" end="5045457082t" region="region0" style="style0">그 아이들 모두에게<br/>책임이 있다고 생각해요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle151" begin="5048793750t" end="5065060000t" region="region0" style="style0">적어도 그 아이들은</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle152" begin="5073401666t" end="5092170416t" region="region0" style="style0">본인이 원하는 선택을 했지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle153" begin="5105100000t" end="5113441666t" region="region0" style="style0">그리고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle154" begin="5120115000t" end="5131376250t" region="region0" style="style0">그 결과를</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle155" begin="5138883750t" end="5150145000t" region="region0" style="style0">받아들인 것뿐이야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle156" begin="5154732916t" end="5163908750t" region="region0" style="style0">그런데</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle157" begin="5180175000t" end="5188933750t" region="region0" style="style0">넌 뭐지?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle158" begin="5211039166t" end="5219380832t" region="region0" style="style0">저는...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle159" begin="5220215000t" end="5230225000t" region="region0" style="style0">강예림</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle160" begin="5236481250t" end="5254832916t" region="region0" style="style0">네가 진정으로 원하는 게 뭘까?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle161" begin="5266511250t" end="5284445832t" region="region0" style="style0">그 아이들을 찾고 싶어 하는</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle162" begin="5300712082t" end="5309887916t" region="region0" style="style0">이유 말이야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle163" begin="5312390416t" end="5335330000t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]<br/>[삐 소리가 귓가에 맴돈다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle164" begin="5352430416t" end="5370782082t" region="region0" style="style0">[괴상한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle165" begin="5470882082t" end="5479640832t" region="region0" style="style0">[놀라는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle166" begin="5520097916t" end="5528439582t" region="region0" style="style0">[살짝 웃는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle167" begin="5529273750t" end="5545540000t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림의 혼란스러운 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle168" begin="5567228332t" end="5579740832t" region="region0" style="style0">모르겠어요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle169" begin="5592670416t" end="5612690416t" region="region0" style="style0">그러니까 상담이라는 게 있잖니</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle170" begin="5650227916t" end="5658569582t" region="region0" style="style0">거울</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle171" begin="5659403750t" end="5675670000t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 효과음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle172" begin="5685680000t" end="5694021666t" region="region0" style="style0">[놀라는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle173" begin="5704031666t" end="5715710000t" region="region0" style="style0">거울 속에서</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle174" begin="5721966250t" end="5746157082t" region="region0" style="style0">네가 원하는 걸<br/>찾을 수 있을지도 모르지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle175" begin="5757835416t" end="5769930832t" region="region0" style="style0">그리고 만약에</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle176" begin="5787865416t" end="5812056250t" region="region0" style="style0">운이 좋아서<br/>네가 원하는 걸 찾게 된다면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle177" begin="5825402916t" end="5840835000t" region="region0" style="style0">다른 아이들이 다시</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle178" begin="5848342500t" end="5860020832t" region="region0" style="style0">돌아올지도?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle179" begin="5867528332t" end="5876704166t" region="region0" style="style0">[의아한 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle180" begin="5916744166t" end="5937181250t" region="region0" style="style0">이 모래가 다 떨어지기 전에<br/>돌아오면 돼</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle181" begin="5948859582t" end="5962206250t" region="region0" style="style0">못 돌아오면요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle182" begin="5967211250t" end="5981809166t" region="region0" style="style0">거기에 남게 되겠지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle183" begin="6005165832t" end="6015592916t" region="region0" style="style0">자, 선택해</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle184" begin="6043954582t" end="6061055000t" region="region0" style="style0">거울 속으로 들어갈 건지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle185" begin="6062723332t" end="6071899166t" region="region0" style="style0">아니면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle186" begin="6078155416t" end="6094838750t" region="region0" style="style0">모든 걸 다 잊고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle187" begin="6099843750t" end="6118195416t" region="region0" style="style0">교실로 돌아갈 건지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle188" begin="6119863750t" end="6136130000t" region="region0" style="style0">[차분한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle189" begin="6186180000t" end="6194938750t" region="region0" style="style0">[옅은 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle190" begin="6218712500t" end="6227054166t" region="region0" style="style0">할게요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle191" begin="6231225000t" end="6240817916t" region="region0" style="style0">[피식]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle192" begin="6241652082t" end="6261672082t" region="region0" style="style0">[기괴한 효과음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle193" begin="6263340416t" end="6272516250t" region="region0" style="style0">계약</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle194" begin="6283777500t" end="6292536250t" region="region0" style="style0">성립</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle195" begin="6293370416t" end="6305882916t" region="region0" style="style0">[날카로운 효과음]<br/>[아파하는 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle196" begin="6308385416t" end="6321315000t" region="region0" style="style0">[잔잔한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle197" begin="6378872500t" end="6388048332t" region="region0" style="style0">[똑딱]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle198" begin="6427254166t" end="6446440000t" region="region0" style="style0">[쿵 하는 효과음]<br/>[음산한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle199" begin="6553630416t" end="6567394166t" region="region0" style="style0">[기괴한 효과음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle200" begin="6592002082t" end="6611187916t" region="region0" style="style0">[음산한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle201" begin="6806382916t" end="6814724582t" region="region0" style="style0">얘들아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle202" begin="6861854999t" end="6872699166t" region="region0" style="style0">나 안 보여?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle203" begin="6896472916t" end="6904814582t" region="region0" style="style0">얘들아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle204" begin="6911904999t" end="6924000416t" region="region0" style="style0">여기 안 보여?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle205" begin="6936095832t" end="6944437499t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림의 반가운 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle206" begin="6947774166t" end="6956115832t" region="region0" style="style0">상우야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle207" begin="6968628332t" end="6977387082t" region="region0" style="style0">서상우</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle208" begin="6979055416t" end="6992819166t" region="region0" style="style0">나 여기 있잖아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle209" begin="6996155832t" end="7005331666t" region="region0" style="style0">서상우</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle210" begin="7009085416t" end="7020346666t" region="region0" style="style0">나 여기 있어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle211" begin="7022014999t" end="7031190832t" region="region0" style="style0">서상우</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle212" begin="7042452082t" end="7051627916t" region="region0" style="style0">나 안 보여?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle213" begin="7054130416t" end="7064140416t" region="region0" style="style0">서상우...<br/>[상우가 피식 웃는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle214" begin="7067059999t" end="7075401666t" region="region0" style="style0">상우야!</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle215" begin="7131707916t" end="7140883749t" region="region0" style="style0">안 돼</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle216" begin="7170079582t" end="7206782916t" region="region0" style="style0">[두려운 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle217" begin="7225968749t" end="7252662082t" region="region0" style="style0">[망연자실한 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle218" begin="7278521249t" end="7287697082t" region="region0" style="style0">[옅은 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle219" begin="7308551249t" end="7317727082t" region="region0" style="style0">[흐느끼는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle220" begin="7472464999t" end="7481223749t" region="region0" style="style0">[떨리는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle221" begin="7719795416t" end="7729805416t" region="region0" style="style0">[신비로운 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle222" begin="7731056666t" end="7741900832t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>봉구 쌤?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle223" begin="7790282499t" end="7804046249t" region="region0" style="style0">2학년 3반</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle224" begin="7810719582t" end="7821980832t" region="region0" style="style0">예림, 상우</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle225" begin="7912904999t" end="7921246666t" region="region0" style="style0">어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle226" begin="7922080832t" end="7932090832t" region="region0" style="style0">[뛰어가는 발걸음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle227" begin="8235310416t" end="8249908332t" region="region0" style="style0">[분위기가 고조되는 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle228" begin="8335410416t" end="8344586249t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>너...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle229" begin="8357515832t" end="8376284582t" region="region0" style="style0">[수업 종소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle230" begin="8402977916t" end="8412153749t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우의 깊은 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle231" begin="8426751666t" end="8435927499t" region="region0" style="style0">[휴대전화 문자 알림음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle232" begin="8478887082t" end="8494736249t" region="region0" style="style0">[안내 음성]<br/>새로운 음성 메시지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle233" begin="8496821666t" end="8508082916t" region="region0" style="style0">[긴장되는 음악]<br/>[휴대전화 조작음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle234" begin="8523514999t" end="8549791249t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>나 지금 상담실 가는 길</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle235" begin="8559384166t" end="8569811249t" region="region0" style="style0">혹시</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle236" begin="8576067499t" end="8599424166t" region="region0" style="style0">나한테 무슨 일이 생기면...<br/>[휴대전화 조작음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle237" begin="8624032082t" end="8633207916t" region="region0" style="style0">(상미)<br/>뭐야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle238" begin="8634459166t" end="8651559582t" region="region0" style="style0">쌤 오늘 상담 안 하시나 봐</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle239" begin="8652810832t" end="8675333332t" region="region0" style="style0">(혜민)<br/>나 진짜 쌤한테 상담받고 싶었는데</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle240" begin="8676167500t" end="8685343332t" region="region0" style="style0">(아영)<br/>나도</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle241" begin="8689931250t" end="8699524166t" region="region0" style="style0">[뛰어오는 발걸음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle242" begin="8713705000t" end="8722046666t" region="region0" style="style0">[문손잡이를 달그락거린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle243" begin="8722880832t" end="8732056666t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>예림아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle244" begin="8740815416t" end="8750825416t" region="region0" style="style0">예림아!</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle245" begin="8763755000t" end="8773765000t" region="region0" style="style0">예림이 못 봤어, 너희?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle246" begin="8775016250t" end="8783775000t" region="region0" style="style0">[아영의 부정하는 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle247" begin="8787945832t" end="8800875416t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>아씨, 어디 간 거야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle248" begin="8809217082t" end="8817558750t" region="region0" style="style0">(혜민)<br/>아, 상우야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle249" begin="8822980832t" end="8842166666t" region="region0" style="style0">예림이 상담받았다던데?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle250" begin="8843000832t" end="8855096250t" region="region0" style="style0">- 아, 진짜?<br/>- 응</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle251" begin="8863437916t" end="8887211666t" region="region0" style="style0">아, 어디 있는 거야, 강예림<br/>[상우의 거친 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle252" begin="8893050832t" end="8904312082t" region="region0" style="style0">(가짜 예림)<br/>서상우</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle253" begin="8905563332t" end="8920161250t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 효과음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle254" begin="8943935000t" end="8957281666t" region="region0" style="style0">나 보고 싶었어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle255" begin="9008582916t" end="9019427082t" region="region0" style="style0">[안도의 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle256" begin="9030688332t" end="9040281250t" region="region0" style="style0">[활짝 웃는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle257" begin="9057798750t" end="9071979582t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle258" begin="9110351250t" end="9124115000t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>넌 여기 혼자 있어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle259" begin="9139547082t" end="9148305832t" region="region0" style="style0">(어린 예림)<br/>아니</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle260" begin="9162486666t" end="9183757916t" region="region0" style="style0">교실에 있는 언니, 오빠들</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle261" begin="9197104582t" end="9207114582t" region="region0" style="style0">무서워</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle262" begin="9219210000t" end="9230471250t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>거기가 어딘데?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle263" begin="9284275000t" end="9301792500t" region="region0" style="style0">[신비로운 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle264" begin="9391465416t" end="9401058332t" region="region0" style="style0">(어린 예림)<br/>여기는</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle265" begin="9416907500t" end="9435676250t" region="region0" style="style0">어디가 어디인지 모르겠어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle266" begin="9807714582t" end="9816890416t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림의 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle267" begin="9838578750t" end="9848588750t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림의 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle268" begin="9874030832t" end="9891965416t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>[한숨 쉬며]<br/>아, 어떡해</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle269" begin="9911985416t" end="9920327082t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림의 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle270" begin="9937844582t" end="9946603332t" region="region0" style="style0">(어린 예림)<br/>나</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle271" begin="9950357082t" end="9966623332t" region="region0" style="style0">언니 매일 봤다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle272" begin="9974547916t" end="9982889582t" region="region0" style="style0">나를?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle273" begin="9984975000t" end="9998738750t" region="region0" style="style0">맨날 봤어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle274" begin="10007497500t" end="10022929582t" region="region0" style="style0">언니 거울 보는 거</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle275" begin="10039195832t" end="10059632916t" region="region0" style="style0">[애잔한 음악]<br/>(어린 예림)<br/>슬퍼 보였어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle276" begin="10073813750t" end="10109265832t" region="region0" style="style0">언니가 재미있게 살면 좋겠다<br/>생각했지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle277" begin="10129702916t" end="10147220416t" region="region0" style="style0">눈치만 보지 말고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle278" begin="10158064582t" end="10182672500t" region="region0" style="style0">하고 싶은 대로<br/>하고 살면 좋겠다고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle279" begin="10205195000t" end="10213536666t" region="region0" style="style0">[헛웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle280" begin="10227717500t" end="10238144582t" region="region0" style="style0">아니야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle281" begin="10243566666t" end="10258581666t" region="region0" style="style0">나 재미있게 살고 있는데?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle282" begin="10278601666t" end="10288611666t" region="region0" style="style0">거짓말</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle283" begin="10295285000t" end="10312802500t" region="region0" style="style0">하나도 재미없으면서</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle284" begin="10316556250t" end="10331571250t" region="region0" style="style0">[못마땅한 숨을 내쉬며]<br/>아니라니까</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle285" begin="10339078750t" end="10358681666t" region="region0" style="style0">언니는 공부를 왜 하는 거야?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle286" begin="10384957916t" end="10395802082t" region="region0" style="style0">나, 참</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle287" begin="10407480416t" end="10422912500t" region="region0" style="style0">공부를 왜 하냐고?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle288" begin="10435842082t" end="10449188750t" region="region0" style="style0">그야 좋은 대학에 가서...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle289" begin="10450022916t" end="10459198750t" region="region0" style="style0">그래서?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle290" begin="10473796666t" end="10488811666t" region="region0" style="style0">커서 뭐가 될 건데?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle291" begin="10544283750t" end="10553459582t" region="region0" style="style0">야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle292" begin="10561801250t" end="10573896666t" region="region0" style="style0">뭐가 되긴...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle293" begin="10590997082t" end="10605595000t" region="region0" style="style0">언니는 겁쟁이야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle294" begin="10616022082t" end="10633956666t" region="region0" style="style0">사람들 눈치만 보고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle295" begin="10647303332t" end="10666072082t" region="region0" style="style0">커서 뭐가 될지도 모르잖아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle296" begin="10724463750t" end="10734056666t" region="region0" style="style0">[멀어지는 발걸음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle297" begin="10745317916t" end="10757830416t" region="region0" style="style0">야, 어디 가?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle298" begin="10774096666t" end="10783272500t" region="region0" style="style0">아이씨</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle299" begin="10792448332t" end="10802041250t" region="region0" style="style0">[옅은 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle300" begin="10815387916t" end="10839161666t" region="region0" style="style0">아, 좋다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle301" begin="10863769582t" end="10872111250t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>어휴</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle302" begin="10874613750t" end="10891714166t" region="region0" style="style0">아, 그래, 그래, 마누라</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle303" begin="10896719166t" end="10910900000t" region="region0" style="style0">좋은 건 알겠는데</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle304" begin="10915487916t" end="10931337082t" region="region0" style="style0">내려오는 게 좋지 않을까 싶네</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle305" begin="10943432500t" end="10951774166t" region="region0" style="style0">상우야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle306" begin="10975965000t" end="11001407082t" region="region0" style="style0">넌 내일 죽는다면 뭘 하고 싶어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle307" begin="11014336666t" end="11022678332t" region="region0" style="style0">뭐?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle308" begin="11036025000t" end="11047703332t" region="region0" style="style0">서상우 씨</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle309" begin="11050622916t" end="11075230832t" region="region0" style="style0">내일 죽는다면 뭘 하고 싶습니까?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle310" begin="11082321250t" end="11091080000t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우가 피식 웃는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle311" begin="11102341250t" end="11123612500t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>음, 저는 글쎄요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle312" begin="11131954166t" end="11144466666t" region="region0" style="style0">뭘 해야 할까요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle313" begin="11151557082t" end="11161984166t" region="region0" style="style0">수업 제치고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle314" begin="11166989166t" end="11184089582t" region="region0" style="style0">우리 예림이랑 하루 종일 놀기?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle315" begin="11193265416t" end="11203275416t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우의 장난스러운 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle316" begin="11209948750t" end="11224546666t" region="region0" style="style0">그럼 예림 씨는</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle317" begin="11234973750t" end="11247903332t" region="region0" style="style0">뭘 하고 싶으신가요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle318" begin="11253325416t" end="11267923332t" region="region0" style="style0">[잔잔한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle319" begin="11290445832t" end="11298787500t" region="region0" style="style0">[살짝 웃는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle320" begin="11312551250t" end="11323812500t" region="region0" style="style0">[CD플레이어 작동음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle321" begin="11334239582t" end="11348837500t" region="region0" style="style0">[익살스러운 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle322" begin="11403475416t" end="11417656250t" region="region0" style="style0">예쁘네<br/>[살짝 웃는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle323" begin="11461032916t" end="11476047916t" region="region0" style="style0">뭐야, 강예림</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle324" begin="11659147500t" end="11667489166t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우의 난처한 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle325" begin="11668323332t" end="11682504166t" region="region0" style="style0">아, 예, 예림아<br/>[학생들의 환호]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle326" begin="11863101250t" end="11878116250t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>죽기 전에 해 보고 싶은 게</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle327" begin="11884789582t" end="11894382500t" region="region0" style="style0">이거였어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle328" begin="11916070832t" end="11935256666t" region="region0" style="style0">(가짜 예림)<br/>[살짝 웃으며]<br/>이거 말고도 많지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle329" begin="11938593332t" end="11951522916t" region="region0" style="style0">지금을 즐겨</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle330" begin="11992814166t" end="12013668332t" region="region0" style="style0">[음산한 음악]<br/>(예림)<br/>야, 같이 가자, 좀</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle331" begin="12055793750t" end="12065803750t" region="region0" style="style0">(어린 예린)<br/>저기</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle332" begin="12083321250t" end="12104592500t" region="region0" style="style0">무서운 오빠, 언니들</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle333" begin="12111265832t" end="12120441666t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>얘들아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle334" begin="12149220416t" end="12157562082t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림의 놀라는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle335" begin="12172994166t" end="12192597082t" region="region0" style="style0">[학생들의 웃음이 들린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle336" begin="12219707500t" end="12238059166t" region="region0" style="style0">[실성한 듯한 웃음이 들린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle337" begin="12259330416t" end="12272677082t" region="region0" style="style0">[실성한 듯한 웃음이 들린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle338" begin="12287275000t" end="12307295000t" region="region0" style="style0">[엔딩곡]</p>
